3	# Design: Home
4	
5	Generate the HTML design mockup for **Home** using the **Flutter HTML Glossary** constrained vocabulary.
6	
7	## Critical Constraint
8	
9	The HTML MUST use ONLY elements from the **Flutter HTML Glossary** (`stitch-flutter/references/flutter-html-glossary.md`). This ensures the `stitch-flutter` converter can produce pixel-perfect Flutter widgets mechanically.
10	
11	## Inputs
12	- `.stitch/designs/home/SPEC.md` — Screen specification
13	- `.stitch/system/DESIGN.md` — Design system
14	- `.stitch/system/META.md` — Reference examples metadata
15	
16	## Steps
17	
18	1. **Read spec** — Load `.stitch/designs/home/SPEC.md` to understand layout, sections, data
19	2. **Read glossary** — Load `stitch-flutter/references/flutter-html-glossary.md` to understand the constrained vocabulary
20	3. **Select best example match** — Read `.stitch/system/META.md` and score against examples per `stitch-generate/references/selecting-examples.md`
21	4. **Read matched reference** — Study the matching example's patterns
22	5. **Generate META.md** — Write `.stitch/designs/home/META.md` with example selection and scoring table
23	6. **Generate design.html** — Write `.stitch/designs/home/design.html` following `stitch-generate` skill using ONLY glossary elements
24	
25	## Glossary Quick Reference
26	
27	- Layout: `.column`, `.row`, `.stack`, `.wrap`, `.expanded`, `.padding`, `.sized-box`
28	- Scaffold: `.scaffold`, `.app-bar`, `.body`, `.bottom-nav`, `.fab`
29	- Text: `.title-large`, `.body-medium`, `.label-small` (Material 3 TextTheme classes)
30	- Components: `.card`, `.chip`, `.list-tile`, `.divider`, `.badge`, `.avatar`
31	- Buttons: `.elevated-btn`, `.filled-btn`, `.text-btn`, `.icon-btn`
32	- Images: `.network-image`, `.placeholder-image`
33	- Icons: `<svg class="icon" data-name="{material_icon}" data-size="24">`
34	- Colors: `data-color="primary"`, `data-bg="surface"` (ColorScheme roles)
35	- Spacing: `data-spacing="md"`, `data-p="lg"` (token names)
36	- Animation: `data-animate="fade-in"`, `data-animate-delay="100"`
37	- Navigation: `.ink-well` with `data-route="/path"`
38	
39	## Output
40	
41	- `.stitch/designs/home/META.md` — Example selection and scoring
42	- `.stitch/designs/home/design.html` — Self-contained HTML mockup at 375px using glossary vocabulary
